parts.text:
```json
{
  "application": "SpecFEM3D",
  "software_requirements": [
    "OpenMPI",
    "Intel compiler",
    "xmeshfem3D",
    "xgenerate_databases",
    "xspecfem3D",
    "xcubedsphere_topo",
    "xcubedsphere_topo_FindOcean"
  ],
  "resource_requirements": {
    "nodes": "${NNODE}",
    "processors_per_node": 16,
    "walltime": "18:00:00"
  },
  "other_requirements": [
    "PBS batch system",
    "DATA directory with model files",
    "OUTPUT_FILES directory for output",
    "Par_file with NPROC defined"
  ],
  "description": "This script runs a seismic simulation using the SpecFEM3D software. It prepares the input files, generates the mesh, creates databases, and runs the simulation. The script uses a PBS batch system to manage the execution on a cluster.",
  "workflow": [
    "Prepare input files and directories",
    "Generate topography files",
    "Run meshing with xmeshfem3D",
    "Generate databases with xgenerate_databases",
    "Run seismic simulation with xspecfem3D"
  ]
}
```
